<span id="freeTextContainer11623759240789490650">Oh the <b>humanity</b>…the expectation-murdering <b>ugh</b> of the <b>dreadful sequel</b> to the quality original. Unfortunately they happen. Some are a <b>menace</b> to the <b>phantoms</b> of our youthful memories:<br/><a href='http://s153.photobucket.com/albums/s207/sullypython/Hollywood%20moviess/?action=view&amp;current=220px-Star_Wars_Phantom_Menace_poster-1.jpg' target='_blank' rel='nofollow noopener'>
