</a><br><br>…others make us long for murderous <b>Revenge</b> on the studio that spawned it from their retched, greed-dripping <b>Jaws</b>.<br><a href="http://s153.photobucket.com/albums/s207/sullypython/Hollywood%20moviess/?action=view&amp;current=220px-Jaws_the_revenge-1.jpg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
