</a><br><br>Some sequels have plot/acting/directing so loaded with <b>mockery- needed fail</b> that we are transformed into staunch proponents of the virtues of <b>franchise euthanasia</b>:<br><a href="http://s153.photobucket.com/albums/s207/sullypython/Hollywood%20moviess/?action=view&amp;current=imagesCAND68CI-1.jpg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
