          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/50868880-reliquary">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55220093-klaas-bottelier?shelf=z-read-in-2020">z-read-in-2020</a>, 
